summary: This is an email chain from May 2020 between FBI personnel, including a Forensic Accountant and a Senior Financial Investigator, discussing the investigation of a property owned by an LLC linked to Ghislaine Maxwell. The emails detail the property's purchase and sale dates, prices, and involved entities.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The property in question is owned by an LLC that may have been partially or fully owned by her. She is the central subject of the financial inquiry.

events.title: Property purchased by LLC
events.description: An LLC, potentially linked to Ghislaine Maxwell, purchased a property. The consideration is noted as nominal, requiring further investigation.

events.title: Property sold by LLC
events.description: The LLC sold the property for $15,075,000 to buyers identified as another LLC.

locations: FBI New York Field Office NYC, NY 10278
keyFacts: An LLC potentially owned by Ghislaine Maxwell purchased a property on July 6, 2000, for a nominal consideration.
The same LLC sold the property on April 14, 2016, for $15,075,000 to another LLC.
The FBI's Forensic Accountant and Squad C-40 (FAST) Senior Financial Investigator were actively investigating this property transaction in May 2020.
The document is part of a financial investigation into Ghislaine Maxwell's assets and transactions.
